import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

    (50.91, 18.41),
    (57.39, 58.34),
    (25.82, 45.12),
    (33.11, 31.36),
    (26.90, 27.04),
    (29.87, 20.84),

# Add the polygon to the plot

# Set the limits and aspect ratio

ax.set_ylim(15, 60)
ax.set_aspect('equal', 'box')

# Add grid for better visualization
ax.grid(True)

# Show the plot
plt.title("SVG Path Visualization")
plt.xlabel("X")
plt.ylabel("Y")
plt.show()
